pantera's <pant> to buy ten pizza restaurants
    st. louis, mo., march 25 - 
pantera's corp said it agreed to buy ten pizza restaurants in
southeastern colorado from creditors foreclosing on the facilities.
the purchase price includes 1.25 mln dlrs in cash and company stock,
it said. separately, pantera's said it issued an area development
agreement with a franchisee group for northeastern colorado, including
the denver area, for the opening of about 20 franchised pantera's
pizza restaurants. reuter 
